snippet.title: Starmancer - Starting a Station | Exclusive Pre-Alpha Gameplay with Developer Commentary Part 1
snippet.description:
Welcome to the first part of our Starmancer Pre-Alpha Special! 

We invited Tyler, programmer of Starmancer to the show and he brought an early version on the game.
Starmancer is a space station management game currently in development, similar to Dwarf Fortress or Rimworld.

Support the Kickstarter here:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1424711375/starmancer/description

For more information check:
https://www.playstarmancer.com/
https://twitter.com/starmancergame

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

You can find us on Twitter:

https://twitter.com/SchematicsTeam

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
